On Escalation Ticket # 00436620 the new comment has been added: Augustina Sidor:

Hi Flaviu,

Please verify on the backend if the WIN agents are available in the software directory. (/EPPServer/sieratool/web/software).


If they are, check the file permissions and ownership.
The expected owner should be www-data:www-data with permissions set to 755.


If they are missing, please inject them on the server and pay attention to the agents' versions. 


If the problem is not solved doing the above steps, please provide some screenshots with the content of the software director and the result of the next query:



--- CODE ---
SELECT * FROM clientsoftware WHERE isdefault = 1;

--- CODE ---





Regards,
Augustina
